This paper discusses methods for finding answers to questions on community forums, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Sound and Music Computing (cs.SD), and Computers and Society (cs.CY).
